### ===========================================
### MIDTRANS PAYMENT GATEWAY - TEST FILE
### ===========================================
### Install "REST Client" extension di VSCode untuk run test ini
### Atau copy-paste ke Postman/Thunder Client

@baseURL = http://localhost:3001/api

### 1. CREATE VIRTUAL ACCOUNT - BCA
POST {{baseURL}}/payments/midtrans/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "bank": "bca"
}

### 2. CREATE VIRTUAL ACCOUNT - BNI
POST {{baseURL}}/payments/midtrans/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "bank": "bni"
}

### 3. CREATE VIRTUAL ACCOUNT - MANDIRI
POST {{baseURL}}/payments/midtrans/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "bank": "mandiri"
}

### 4. CREATE VIRTUAL ACCOUNT - BRI
POST {{baseURL}}/payments/midtrans/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "bank": "bri"
}

### ===========================================
### SIMULATE PAYMENT SUCCESS (WEBHOOK)
### ===========================================
### Ganti order_id dengan yang didapat dari response create VA di atas

POST {{baseURL}}/payments/midtrans/notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "BOOKING-1-1234567890",
  "transaction_status": "settlement",
  "payment_type": "bank_transfer",
  "transaction_id": "test-transaction-123",
  "fraud_status": "accept",
  "gross_amount": "500000"
}

### ===========================================
### CHECK TRANSACTION STATUS
### ===========================================
### Ganti order_id dengan yang didapat dari response create VA

GET {{baseURL}}/payments/midtrans/status/BOOKING-1-1234567890

### ===========================================
### NOTES:
### ===========================================
### 1. Pastikan backend server running (npm run dev)
### 2. Pastikan ada data booking dengan id=1 di database
### 3. Untuk test real payment:
###    a. Run test #1-4 untuk dapat VA number
###    b. Buka https://simulator.sandbox.midtrans.com/
###    c. Pilih Bank Transfer
###    d. Masukkan VA number
###    e. Klik Pay
###    f. Webhook akan otomatis dipanggil Midtrans
